# Colophon

I use the Emacs text editor with visual-line-mode to edit the Gemtext of this site, and the Lichen Content Management System to render it to static HTML files, using a Forth program run using Gforth, GNU Forth 0.7.3 (NOT the bleeding edge version), and a couple of bash scripts to run the Forth program.

